\add* good in thy sight. And Hezekiah wept sore.
\p
\v 4 Then came the word of the LORD to Isaiah, saying, 
\v 5 Go, and say to Hezekiah, Thus saith the LORD, the God of David thy
father, I have heard thy prayer, I have seen thy tears: behold, I will add
