\v 19 So shall they fear the name of the LORD from the west, and his glory
from the rising of the sun. When the enemy shall come in like a flood, the
Spirit of the LORD shall lift up a standard against him.
\p
\v 20 And the Redeemer shall come to Zion, and unto them that turn from
transgression in Jacob, saith the LORD. 
\v 21 As for me, this \add is\add* my covenant with them, saith the LORD; My
